{"type":null,"faqId":46220,"title":"如何启用数字密码锁定屏幕？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、设置&gt;隐私和安全&gt;锁屏和密码&gt;锁屏密码&gt;数字密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、在提示框中输入数字密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、再次输入数字密码，点击确定完成数字密码的设定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当点电源键或开关机时，左右滑动解锁杂志锁屏后，会显示数字密码解锁界面，输入设定的数字密码后自动解除屏幕的锁定。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2000","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376340000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":38,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"PIN码,锁屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}